%8F%E8%A7%88%E5%99%A8"><span class="toc-number">1.4.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">浏览器</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#app"><span class="toc-number">1.4.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">APP</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#token%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%98%B2%E5%BE%A1"><span class="toc-number">1.5.</span> <span class="toc-text">Token 安全防御</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%8E%88%E6%9D%83"><span class="toc-number">1.6.</span> <span class="toc-text">微信授权</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%AE%9E%E4%BE%8B"><span class="toc-number">1.7.</span> <span class="toc-text">实例</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#openid"><span class="toc-number">2.</span> <span class="toc-text">OpenID</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#openid%E4%B8%8Eoauth20%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB"><span class="toc-number">2.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">OpenID 与 OAuth2.0 区别</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#jwt"><span class="toc-number">3.</span> <span class="toc-text">JWT</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#jwt%E7%BB%84%E6%88%90"><span class="toc-number">3.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">JWT 组成</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E5%A4%B4%E9%83%A8%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AFheader"><span class="toc-number">3.1.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">头部信息 (header)</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E4%BD%93payload"><span class="toc-number">3.1.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">消息体 payload</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E7%AD%BE%E5%90%8D-signature"><span class="toc-numb